<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:83215">
			
	<ab xml:lang="san-Latn" rendition="class:grantha maturity:83215">		
		<lb n="1"/>śrī
	</ab>
	<p>
		kō-māṟa-paṉmar-āṉa <hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi>vaṉa-ca<hi rend="grantha">kra</hi>-va<reg>r</reg>ttikaḷ Em maṇṭalamuṅ koṇṭ-aruḷiya <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-kulacēkara-tēvarkku yāṇ
		<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṭu <num value="34">3 10+ 4</num>-Āvatu <hi rend="grantha">mi<choice><orig>d</orig><reg>t</reg></choice>hu</hi>na-nāyaṟṟu <hi rend="grantha">pūrvva-<unclear>pakṣa</unclear></hi>ttu <hi rend="grantha">t<choice><sic>ra</sic><corr>ṛ</corr></choice></hi>tiyaiyum putaṉ-kiḻamaiyum peṟṟa puṉar-pūcattu nāḷ
	</p>
	<p>
		tiru-malai-nā
		<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭṭu-t tiru-k-koṭuṅ-kuṉṟattu Uṭaiyār tiru-k-koṭuṅ-kuṉṟam-uṭaiya nāyaṉār-kōyil <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-paṇṭārattārōm
		<lb n="4"/>kīḻ vempa-nāṭṭu Irāca-valli-purattu-k koṉṟai cēr muṭiyaṉ tiru-nelvēli Uṭaiyāṉ-āṉa tacca-vēḷaikkāṟar
		<lb n="5" break="no"/>kku piṭi-pāṭu paṇṇi-k kuṭutta paric' āvatu
	</p>
	<p>
		In-nāyaṉārkkum nalla-maṅkaiyārkkum tām ceyvitta mahā-maṇṭa
		<lb n="6" break="no"/>pattukku Irākkālattil cantiyā-tīpa-t-tiru-viḷakk' iṭuvat' āka vara-k kāṭṭit tiru-viḷakk' iṭaiyar vacam Aṭaitta muṉṉāḷ mu-p
		<lb n="7" break="no"/>-pattu mūṉṟ-āvatu paṅkuṉi-mātam pattān tiyati mutal Aṭaitta Āṭu <num value="275">2 100+ 7 10+ 5</num>-kku Āṭu <num value="50">5 10+</num>-kku nāḷ Oṉṟukku Aḷakkum ⌈
		<lb n="8" break="no"/>ney <g type="undefined"/> Āka ney <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/>-m itaṉ etir-āmm āṇṭu Āṭi-mātam patt' oṉpatān tiyati mutal Aṭaitta Āṭu <num value="212">2 100+ 10+ 2</num>-kku nāḷ
		<lb n="9"/>Oṉṟukku ney <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/>-m muṉṉāḷ mu-p-patt' iraṇṭ-āvatu tai-mātam mutal Aṭaittu-k <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character" precision="low"/> kaṇikkuḷ 5 Irākka
		<lb n="10"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character" precision="low"/> lattil Iṭum viḷakku Aṟupa(tu)kku veṭṭiṉa kalveṭṭu-p paṭi Āṭu <num value="300">3 100+</num> kku ney <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/>-m Ā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character" precision="low"/> <num value="700">7 100+</num> Ārai Ivv-āṭu E
		<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḻu ṉūṟṟ' eḻupatt' ēḻum cāvā mūvā-p pēr-āṭ-āka-k kai-k-koṇṭu nāḷ Oṉṟukku Iṭaiyar Aḷakkum ney <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/>
		<lb n="12"/><g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/> <g type="undefined"/>
	</p>
	<p>
		In-ney muṉṉāḻi mūvuḻak kāḻākkē Iraṇṭ' arai-c ceviṭṭukku nāḻikai Ēḻ' arai Eriya Iṭum tiru-viḷakku-p pa
		<lb n="13" break="no"/>tt' āka-t tiru-vi(ḷa)kku nūṟṟ' aimpatt' ēḻ' araiyum Iṭṭu-p pōtuvōm ākavum
	</p>
	<p>
		Ip-paṭi cantirātitta-vaṟ celvat' āka-k kalli
		<lb n="14" break="no"/>lum cempilu(m) veṭṭi-k koḷvat' ā(ka) piṭi-pāṭu paṇṇi-k kuṭuttōm
		koṉṟai cēr muṭiyaṉ tiru-nelvēli Uṭaiy
		<lb n="15" break="no"/>āṉ-āṉa tacca-vēḷaikkāṟarkku śrī-paṇṭārattārōm
	</p>
	<p>
		<list>
			<item>Ivai <hi rend="grantha">śrī-</hi>kāriyam piṟavāmaṟ kāttāṉ eḻuttu</item>
		<item>Ip-paṭi
		<lb n="16"/>kku vāṉō-pirā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character" precision="low"/> nampiyār eḻuttu</item>
			<item>Ip-paṭikku cuntara-pāṇṭiya-paṭṭar eḻuttu</item>
			<item>nāyakaṉ tiru-nilai-y-aḻakiyāṉ-āṉa tiru
				<lb n="17" break="no"/>malai-nāṭu-paṭṭar eḻuttu</item>
			<item>Ip-paṭikku Ēkāmpara-paṭṭar eḻuttu</item>
			<item>Ip-paṭikku Ivai māṭāpattiyam
				<lb n="18"/>tiru-malai-y-uṭaiyār Eḻuttu</item>
			<item>Ip-paṭikku Ivai tiru-mañcaṇam-uṭaiyāṉ eḻuttu</item>
			<item>Ivai kōyil-kaṇakku tiru-c-ciṟṟampalam-uṭaiyā
				<lb n="19" break="no"/>ṉ Eḻuttu</item>
		</list>
 	</p>
